          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Email us at <a href="mailto:info@gpulse.ai" class="text-cyan underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-cyan-dark transition-colors">info@gpulse.ai</a>, <a href="#feedback" class="text-cyan underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-cyan-dark transition-colors">submit feedback below</a>, or join our <a href="https://discord.gg/nnU28awf" class="text-cyan underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-cyan-dark transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord</a>. We read every message.
